@node "2_12" " SECTION 2 - Modeling and Detail Editor "
 12] May I use more than four textures in Imagine v2.0?

Yes and no, to use more than four textures using Imagine v2.0 You can use 'Add
axis' function, define texture/s (the axis one/s) with 'Apply to children'
gadget on.  Now You can group the axis to the object to avoid four textures
limit, just one note:  this little tip has some side effects with layered
textures, just try it.

